description: The Karibuu Kaizoku-dan are a crew who arrived at Sabaody Archipelago around the same time as the Mugiwara no Ichimi were reuniting. Their captains are the brothers Karibuu and Koribuu, which temporarily changed to Demalo Black when they joined the Nise Mugiwara no Ichimi, under the belief they were real until the truth was disclosed.
name: Karibuu Kaizoku-dan
